fm: int maxNiceDivisors(int primeFactors)      {         if (primeFactors==1) return 1;         if (primeFactors==2) return 2;         if (primeFactors==3) return 3;         if (primeFactors==4) return 4;         int a,b;         if (primeFactors%3==0)         {             a = primeFactors/3;             b = 0;         }         else if (primeFactors%3==2)         {             a = (primeFactors-2)/3;             b = 1;         }         else         {             a = (primeFactors-4)/3;             b = 2;         }         long long ret = 1;         ret = ret * quickMul(3, a) % M;         ret = ret * quickMul(2, b) % M;         return ret;      }

fm: int closestFair(int n)      {                         int count = 0;         int ret = helper(n, count);         if (ret!=-1) return ret;                              while (n>=0)         {             int ret = helper(n+1, count);             if (ret!=-1) return ret;                          ret = helper(n+2, count);             if (ret!=-1) return ret;                          n = n/10;             count++;                         }         return -1;     }
fc: class Solution { public:     int closestFair(int n)      {                         int count = 0;         int ret = helper(n, count);         if (ret!=-1) return ret;                              while (n>=0)         {             int ret = helper(n+1, count);             if (ret!=-1) return ret;                          ret = helper(n+2, count);             if (ret!=-1) return ret;                          n = n/10;             count++;                         }         return -1;     }          int helper(int n, int count)     {         int m = n;         int odd = 0, even = 0;         while (m>0)         {             if (m%2==0)                 even++;             else                 odd++;               m/=10;         }                  int sum = count, diff = odd-even;         if ((sum + diff) % 2 != 0) return -1;         int a = (sum + diff) / 2;   // # of 0         int b = (sum - diff) / 2;   // # of 1                    if (a<0 || b<0) return -1;                      for (int i=0; i<a; i++)             n = n*10 + 0;         for (int i=0; i<b; i++)             n = n*10 + 1;         return n;     } };

fm: int distMoney(int money, int children)      {         if (money < children) return -1;         if (money==4 && children==1) return -1;         if (money > children * 8) return children-1;                  int d = money - children;         int k = d / 7;         int r = d % 7;                  if (r==3 && (children-k)==1)             return k-1;         else             return k;              }
